## ü§ñ Your AI-Powered Workflows

### Creating Workflows

Build automation workflows in `studio/workflows/`. Example:

```yaml
id: daily-newsletter
description: Research trends, write newsletter, distribute everywhere
steps:
  - id: trend-research
    description: AI monitors your industry for trending topics
    prompt: |
      Research the top 3 trending topics in [your industry] today.
      Focus on topics that align with our brand values.
    acceptance_criteria: |
      - Found 3 relevant trending topics
      - Each topic has at least 2 credible sources
      - Topics align with our brand positioning

  - id: newsletter-creation
    description: Write newsletter using our brand voice
    prompt: |
      Write a newsletter using our tone of voice guidelines.
      Include actionable insights for our audience.
    acceptance_criteria: |
      - Newsletter follows our voice guidelines
      - Includes clear call-to-action
      - Provides genuine value to readers
```

### Managing Workflows with AI

Your Cursor AI agent can help you:

- **`list-workflows`** - See all your automation workflows
- **`start-workflow`** - Begin any workflow process
- **`next-step`** - Continue workflow execution

Simply tell your AI: *"Start my daily newsletter workflow"* and watch it execute.

